  p And he's right. ‚ÄúThe committee‚Äù are afraid of rocking the boat. These ads are the product of!{' '}
    span.bold an individuals vision
    | .
  p My second observation is that!{' '}
    span.bold the product is unimportant
    | . There is nothing special about flea markets, razor blades, or roller skating. The common thread is humour.
  p To quote Howard Gossage, ‚ÄúNobody watches ads. People watch what entertains them. Sometimes it's an ad‚Äù.
